-----------
| Files |
________________________________________________________________________________________________________

   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-img/			| images
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-js/			| JavaScript
   |--main.js			| global JavaScript
   |--mootools*core.js	| the MooTools core
   |--mootools*more.js	| the MooTools more
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-jsClasses/		| JavaScript Classes
   |--Lightbox.js			| Lightbox class - adds "toggleable" layers to the page
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-jsDocs/		| JavaScript Documentation
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-logs/			| Error logs
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-php/			| PHP Scripts
   |--includes.php		| class includes and session initialization
   |--login.php			| simple php login script using the User and Database classes
   |--signup.php		| simple php signup script using the User and Database classes
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-phpClasses/	| PHP Classes
   |--Database.php		| DatabaseConnection class
   |--Filters.php			| User input filtering class
   |--htmLawed1.1.9.1	| Html Sanitizer
   |--Security.php		| User Authentication Check
   |--Template.php		| Allows for seperation of data gathering and presentation logic
   |--User.php			| Class for user management
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-phpDocs/		| PHP Documentation
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-SQL/			| for reference: any SQL statements needed for site database
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-style/			| CSS Styles
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-templates/		| Page Templates
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |--index.php		| main site
   |--MooKit.dia		| MooKit Dia diagram
   |--README		| this file
   |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
